    <chapter>
        <header>About the metadata catalog</header>
        <section help-key="about-1">
            <header>Portrait</header>
            <content>
                <p>This metadata catalog is provided by the Federal Highway and Transport Research Institute (BASt).</p>
                <p>The mission statement of the BASt and further information can be found on the
                <a href="https://www.bast.de/EN/BASt/e-Leitbild.html">BASt website</a>.</p>
                <p>Proclaimer: For further information, look into the extended German version or get in touch with opendata@bast.de</p>
            </content>
        </section>
        <section help-key="about-2">
            <header>Information providers</header>
            <content>
                <p>The metadata catalog is used to search for information on existing or
                planned datasets from the BASt, as well as possible access to
                external data sources.</p>
                <p>The content is created and maintained centrally by BASt Open Data Coordination (see imprint).</p>
            </content>
        </section>
    </chapter>
    <chapter>
        <header>Search</header>
        <section help-key="search-1">
            <header>Search input</header>
            <content>
                <p>To search something, enter one or more terms in the search field and then click the button 
                <b>SEARCH</b>.</p>
                <p>The metadata catalog searches all embedded information.
                The result of your search is displayed in a
                   <a href="?hkey=search-results-1">search results page</a>.</p>
                <p>Further restrictions can be specified on the left side.
                Any number of restrictions can be selected and deselected.
                The “delete all restrictions” button removes all restrictions.</p>
            </content>
        </section>
    </chapter>
